# VoxBulk organisation roles

Source of truth: `voxbulk-api/app/services/org_rbac.py` and `dashboard-web/src/lib/org-roles.ts`.

## Roles (per organisation)

| Role | Campaigns | Billing | Team invite/remove |
|------|-----------|---------|-------------------|
| **owner** | Full | Full | Yes |
| **manager** | Full | Full | Yes |
| **accountant** | View only (no billing API) | Full | No |
| **member** | Run campaigns | No | No |
| **receptionist** | Recovery / calls | No | No |

## Multi-company

- One login can belong to multiple orgs (`OrganisationMembership` rows).
- JWT carries active `org_id`. Switch via `POST /auth/switch-organisation`.
- Login with 2+ orgs returns `org_selection_required` + organisation list.

## Team invites

- Email template: `team_invite` (not `general_notification`).
- Accept: `GET /auth/invite-preview`, `POST /auth/accept-invite` (public sign-in with `?invite_token=`).
- Logged-in accept: `POST /auth/accept-invite-session`.

## Email theme

- All transactional templates use `wrap_brand_email` from `brand_email_layout.py`.
- Keys: `team_invite`, `weekly_digest`, billing lifecycle, interview templates.
